        <p>A member of our Code for Good team will be in touch to get a conversation started. We hope to work with you!</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Volunteers</h2>
    <p>For volunteers, Weekend for Good provides a unique opportunity to connect with the local tech and design community. A typical Weekend for Good draws 100 to 150 volunteers. Individuals can work with their colleagues in company teams, or they can opt to be matched with fellow volunteers who have complementary skill sets.</p>
    <p>Everyone is welcome to head home for the evenings – but there are always the diehards who work from Friday kickoff straight through Sunday afternoon. Food and drinks, especially of the caffeinated variety, are provided, along with game systems for breaks.</p>

